USER.md
SOUL.md
IDENTITY.md
AGENTS.md
BOOTSTRAP.md
HEARTBEAT.md
TOOLS.md
memory/

# Nested skills (this repo IS the skill, not a container)
skills/auto-evolve/
skills/.iterations/
skills/.learnings/

